        "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nOn the Portfolio page, the footer section contains links that are currently broken. Clicking any of these links results in a 404 Not Found error. The styling of the footer is correct and should not be altered; only the link targets need to be fixed.\n\n### To Reproduce\n\nTo Reproduce\n\n1. Go to the Home page.\n2. Navigate to the Portfolio page.\n3. Scroll to the footer section.\n4. Click any link in the footer.\n5. Observe that the links lead to 404 pages.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nAll footer links on the Portfolio page should point to valid pages and function correctly, without altering the footer’s styling.\n\n### Additional context\n\nActual behavior\nThe footer links are broken and return 404 Not Found errors.\n\nType of Issue\n\n-  Bug\n-  Enhancement\n-  UI/UX Improvement\n\nSuggested Fix\nUpdate the hrefs of the footer links to point to valid pages. Ensure that the visual styling of the footer remains unchanged.\n\nEnvironment\nPage: Portfolio\nSection: Footer\nBrowser: All\nMode: Both Light and Dark",
