        "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nOn the Home page, the footer section appears unstyled. The HTML content is rendered as raw elements without any CSS styling applied. This causes the footer to look inconsistent with the rest of the page’s design.\n\n### To Reproduce\n\nTo Reproduce\n\n- Open the site’s Home page.\n- Scroll to the bottom of the page to view the footer section.\n- Observe that the footer content is displayed without styling.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nThe footer section should have styling applied to match the existing workflow and design language of the Home page, appearing consistent with the rest of the site’s layout and theme.\n\n### Additional context\n\nI am a contributor from hacktoberfest'25, kindly assign me this issue to work on it.",
