        "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nOn the home page under the “Services” section, the Content Writing card shows two buttons — “Read More” and “Explore”. The “Explore” button renders without any visible text label, resulting in a blank button.\n\n### To Reproduce\n\nTo Reproduce\n\nGo to the site’s Home page.\n\nScroll to the “Services” section.\n\nLocate the “Content Writing” card.\n\nObserve the two buttons — “Read More” has text, the second button is blank (should be “Explore”).\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nBoth buttons should render with their proper text labels. The second button should display “Explore” instead of rendering blank.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
